Community Impact
Fortive’s culture of caring at Specialty Product Technologies was evident in the harrowing week following Hurricane Matthew. At every level of the company, people helped each other. Fortive sent truckloads of food and donations to the United Way. Company managers personally checked in with each associate and communicated a “family first, work second” mentality. Team members helped each other with bedding and clothing donations.




 









 

Careers at Fortive
At Fortive there’s no limit to what you can learn, or the impact you can make. And there’s no need to choose between the excitement of a startup and the opportunities made possible by a global business with a strong history of success. At Fortive you can work with and learn from the best.

