Strategic Segments






Fortive’s businesses represent the very best of their industries. Individually, they have long histories of innovating to solve their customers’ most pressing challenges. Together, they deliver essential technology that accelerates progress in a range of dynamic and exciting fields.

Fortive’s operating companies are organized into two strategic segments:













 



Professional Instrumentation
Our professional instrumentation businesses specialize in advanced measurement and monitoring to keep critical infrastructure up and running, turn innovative concepts into finished products and deliver valuable business intelligence.




Field Solutions*
Product Realization*
Sensing Technologies






 



Industrial Technologies
Our industrial technologies businesses supply high-tech equipment, components, software and services to the manufacturing, transportation and repair markets worldwide. These industry-leading businesses keep global fleets moving, automate industrial processes through precision robotics and provide high-end diagnostics.




Transportation Technologies
Automation & Specialty
Franchise Distribution









*Part of Advanced Instrumentation & Solutions


























